IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User paul.rougieux@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass gmail"
TLSType IMAPS  # Updated from SSLType
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
# Expunge Both removes messages that are marked as deleted on both sides, so
# that server-side deletions become effective instead of just flagged.
Expunge Both
SyncState *


